    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a functional, reliable daily driver. While the engine and transmission are operational, the car shows clear signs of age, including noticeable cosmetic wear on the exterior paint and some stains on the interior upholstery. It has been regularly serviced, but a prospective buyer should expect to address minor maintenance items and general wear-and-tear in the near future. This is a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly vehicle that still has plenty of life left.",
      "price": 20000.0,
