    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in solid, good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. While the exterior paint still holds a nice shine, you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. The interior is clean and comfortable, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster and minor scuffing on the door sills. Mechanically, the car is sound, with a complete service history and tires that have plenty of tread remaining. It is a reliable, attractive vehicle that is ready for its next owner without needing any immediate repairs.",
      "price": 34500.0,
