    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that won't break the bank? This vehicle is a solid, functional choice that's ready for its next adventure! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, it remains a reliable driver that gets the job done. It's the perfect opportunity to own a capable car at a great price\u2014ideal for anyone who values practicality and character!",
